org.openntf.domino.logging

Class JSONFormatter

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.logging.Formatter
      • org.openntf.domino.logging.JSONFormatter

  • public class JSONFormatter
extends java.util.logging.Formatter
    JSONFormatter class for outputting logs as JSON objects. Not used currently and should probably be replaced with Java classes better designed to write JSON rather than building content up with a StringBuilder
